tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE vehicle_emissions(
    vehicle_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    vehicle_type VARCHAR(50),
    emission_level DECIMAL(10, 2),
    date_recorded DATE
)

CREATE TABLE vehicle_emissions (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    vehicle_type VARCHAR(50),
    model VARCHAR(50),
    year INT,
    emissions_level DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE emission_testing (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    vehicle_id INT,
    testing_date DATE,
    tester_name VARCHAR(100),
    passed BOOLEAN
);

CREATE TABLE vehicle_info (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    vehicle_type VARCHAR,
    make VARCHAR,
    model VARCHAR,
    year INT,
    emission_level DECIMAL
)

CREATE TABLE emission_data (
    data_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    vehicle_id INT,
    emission_rate DECIMAL,
    recorded_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE location_data (
    location_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    vehicle_id INT,
    city VARCHAR,
    state VARCHAR,
    country VARCHAR
)

CREATE TABLE emissions_standards (
    standard_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    standard_name VARCHAR,
    limit DECIMAL
)

CREATE TABLE vehicle_manufacturers (
    manufacturer_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    manufacturer_name VARCHAR,
    country VARCHAR
)
